name: Filling void, Silhouette 1/2, 2021
description:
watercolors, acrylic, digital print on old paper, coffee and collage hannemuhle paper, cm 20x30
part of the series Filling Void, a collection of mixed media works started mid 2020 trying to investigate the opposite concepts of full and void with painting, collage and digital print, in this case the silhouette of a man
